WEBVTT

00:10:28.790 --> 00:10:31.210
a zapravo postoji neko
ko gradi drugi sprat

00:10:31.210 --> 00:10:32.820
ispred kuće čike Ibrahima,

00:10:32.820 --> 00:10:35.070
tako da prekriva deo slike,

00:10:35.070 --> 00:10:37.656
pa ću možda morati
da se vratim i oslikam ga.

00:10:37.680 --> 00:10:39.296
(Smeh)

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:40.696
U pitanju je bilo iskustvo,

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:42.136
priča,

00:10:42.160 --> 00:10:43.440
trenutak.

00:10:44.560 --> 00:10:46.456
Sa ulica susedstva,

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:48.100
slika se javlja u delićima,

00:10:48.124 --> 00:10:50.016
međusobno izolovanim,

00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:51.296
koji stoje sami,

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:53.496
ali povezani znakom kaligrafije

00:10:53.520 --> 00:10:57.376
koji danas otkriva moćnu poruku
da svi mi treba da promislimo

00:10:57.400 --> 00:10:59.080
pre nego što osudimo nekoga.

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:01.776
Svako ko želi da jasno vidi
svetlost sunca